quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  21,11,"Kodi ndi mizinda ingati imene tidaononga imene idali yochita zoipa, ndipo m’malo mwawo tidaikamo anthu ena"
  21,12,Ndipo pamene iwo adaona chilango chathu iwo adayesa kuthawa m’mizinda yawo
  21,13,“Musathawe koma bwererani kumene mumakhala moyo wa chisangalalo ndi ku nyumba zanu kuti mukafunsidwe.”
  21,14,"Iwo anati, “Tsoka kwa ife! Ndithudi tinali kuchita zoipa.”"
  21,15,Koma kulira kwawo sikunathe mpaka pamene Ife tidawaononga ndi kukhala ngati munda umene wakololedwa
  21,16,Sitidalengemwamasewerakumwambandidzikolapansi ndi zonse zimene zili pakati pake
  21,17,"Ife tikadafuna kuti tisangalale tikadadzipangira tokha, ngati Ife tikadafunadi kutero"
  21,18,"Iyayi! Ife timatumiza choonadi kuti chilimbane ndi bodza ndipo chimaliononga. Taonani, ilo latha. Ndipo tsoka kwa inu chifukwa cha zimene mumanena"
  21,19,Zake ndi zonse zimene zili kumwamba ndi pa dziko lapansi. Ndipo onse amene ali pafupi pake sanyozera kumupembedza Iye ndipo satopa ayi
  21,20,Iwo amamutamanda Iye masana ndi usiku ndipo sachita ulesi
  21,21,Kodi iwo asankha milungu ya pa dziko lapansi imene imadzutsa anthu akufa
  21,22,"Kukadakhala milungu ina kumeneko yoonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni, ndithudi, konse kukadaonongeka. Alemekezeke Mulungu, Mwini wa Mpando wa Chifumu, mu zimene akumunenera"
  21,23,Iye sangafunsidwe pa ntchito zimene amachita pamene iwo adzafunsidwa
  21,24,"Kodi kapena iwo asankha milungu ina yoonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni? Nena, “Bweretsani umboni wanu”. Ichi ndi chikumbutso cha amene ndili nawo ndiponso iwo amakedzana. Koma ambiri a iwo sadziwa choonadi motero salabadira"
  21,25,"Ndipo Ife sitidatumize iwe usadabadwe, Mtumwi wina aliyense amene sitinamuuze kuti, “Kulibe Mulungu wina koma Ine ndekha, kotero ndi pembedzeni Ine.”"
  21,26,"Iwo amati, “Mwini chisoni chosatha wabereka mwana wamwamuna.” Iye alemekezedwe! Amenewo si ena ayi koma akapolo ake olemekezeka"
  21,27,"Iwo sayankhula pokhapokha Iye atayankhula, ndipo amachita zinthu potsatira malamulo ake"
  21,28,Iye amadziwa zonse zimene zili patsogolo pawo ndiponso zimene zili m’mbuyo mwawo ndipo iwo sangalankhulire wina aliyense chipulumutso kupatula amene Iye wamukonda ndipo iwo amanjenjemera chifukwa cha mantha pomuona Iye
  21,29,"Ndipo ngati wina wa iwo atanena kuti, “Ndithudi ine ndine mulungu kuonjezera pa Iye.” Oteroyo adzalangidwa ndi moto wa ku Gahena. Mmenemo ndi mmene timalipirira anthu olakwa"